  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, effects of γδT cells on human breast cancer (her2-, er-,pr-) in combination
      with tumor reducing surgery, for example cryosurgery going to be investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Breast tumor will be removed using tumor reducing surgery such as cryosurgery. PBMC of the
      patient will be separated from peripheral blood. After making them potential cancer killer γδ
      T Cell and DC-CIK, they will be infused to the patients as immunotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
